{"tid":826080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打風後學校停課飯商捐出1.5萬飯盒 大埔免費派街坊","createTime":"2018-09-18T03:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T04:13:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca22eae18ec3a2449434ea1c3bc36c207f8080c3","tid":826080,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537239250_571d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537239250_571d.jpg&h=57767b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537239250_0fbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537239250_0fbb.jpg&h=fd474e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537239503_af07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537239503_af07.jpg&h=a77dd564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風山竹襲港後，本港中小學及幼稚園昨日及今日一連停課兩天，有飯商供應商積壓了1.5萬個飯盒無法送出，為免浪費亦為了幫助市民，遂決定免費送出該批飯盒。慈善食物回收商及循道衛理聯合教會遂聯合派出義工幫忙，並於今晨11時至1時，在大埔富亨邨亨翠樓的大埔循道衛理幼稚園，向市民免費派發1.5萬飯盒，獲網民紛紛讚好。<br />\n<br />\n有份協助派飯的循道衛理聯合教會大埔堂職員指，今次免費派飯目的有二，一是為免浪費，二是希望幫助有需要的市民，故可容許排隊長每人取多於一個飯盒（可與家人分享）。他強調飯盒是衛生的，但為了保鮮曾經冷藏，故需要先經翻熱才可食用，惟飯盒先到先得，送完即止。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》現場直擊，見到未至上午11時，已有數十名街坊包括大人小孩排隊領取飯盒，眾人均面露笑容，排隊秩序良好。<br />\n<br />\n記者黃麗英<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180918/58694308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694308&d=9m%2FyOCgkafFPAhLMJX9bnttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b44a2ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180918%2F58694308&h=5a884dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180918/58694308</a>"},{"pid":"febcaa7cb2805eeaeff6a6ee239fd06711a5256f","tid":826080,"uid":334,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"等佢地知道小學生每日都係食呢啲垃圾"},{"pid":"b15d12184516a9f30990a9fb94abaafb5e1e729a","tid":826080,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"好過賣廣告"},{"pid":"67e3c6882bff781d3021c77d583d28f054b9d6e9","tid":826080,"uid":168156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"又益左班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fd35d29b4cb1b810cbdeedc5d6d4192bf59c57","tid":826080,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"邊間呀 幫人賣個廣告都好呀"},{"pid":"d6f23cb101978ec3e29315656cf2599384833cda","tid":826080,"uid":72009,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537239250_e8ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537239250_e8ed.jpg&h=f17dedb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾正，想排隊"},{"pid":"d4cde16f850d703a83136f4645133395d08f068c","tid":826080,"uid":54012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"狗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bb0d9f23f6a9d54d3a3cfd2823dbef19384af9","tid":826080,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"活力午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dee03703598e5b6f6caadc67cafa26c270d75a","tid":826080,"uid":167809,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d6f2